{"word":"ἠρεμήρης","slug":"ἠρεμήρης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n47546\" key=\"h)remh/rhs\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἠρεμ-ήρης</orth>, an <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adj.\">Adj.</a></pos> termin., <sense n=\"1\" id=\"n47546.0\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> from <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀραρ-εῖν, ἀραρ-ίσκω</foreign>, as in <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">θυμαρής, φρενήρης, χαλκήρης, εὐήρης</foreign>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n47546.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> from <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐρε- </foreign>(<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἐρέ-της</etym>), as in <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀμφήρης, ἁλιήρης, τριήρης</foreign>, etc. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n47546.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> prob. from (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ϝ</etym>)<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ηρ-</foreign> (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἦρα</foreign> B) in pr.n. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Περιήρης, Διώρης</foreign> (fr. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Διοήρης</foreign>).</sense> </entryFree>"}]}